akos]]\n|-\n| 13 || style=\"text-align: left;\" | [[Drew Holland]] || GK || {{convert|6|ft|5|in|m|abbr=on}} || {{convert|195|lbs|kg|abbr=on}} || R || style=\"text-align: left;\" | {{birth date and age|1995|4|11}} || style=\"text-align: left;\" | [[Stanford University|Stanford]] '17 || style=\"text-align: left;\" | {{flagicon|ESP}} [[CN Caballa]]\n|}\n\n===Former squads===\n{{main|List of United States men's national water polo team rosters}}\n\n====Olympic Games====\n{{main|List of United States men's Olympic water polo team rosters}}\n\n{{div col}}\n* {{flagicon|USA|1896}} [[Water polo at the 1904 Summer Olympics|1904 St. Louis]] \u2013 '''{{Gold1}} Gold''', '''{{Silver2}} Silver''', '''{{Bronze3}} Bronze medals''' (Demonstration event)\n*: [[New York Athletic Club]]: [[David Bratton]], [[Leo Goodwin (swimmer)|Budd Goodwin]], [[Louis Handley]], [[David Hesser]], [[Joe Ruddy]], [[James Steen (water polo)|James Steen]], [[George Van Cleaf]].<ref name=\"1904OG SR\"/> Head coach: [[Gus Sundstrom]].<ref name=\"Gus Sundstrom\"/>\n*: [[Chicago Athletic Association]]: [[Rex Beach]], [[David Hammond (swimmer)|David Hammond]], [[Charles Healy]], [[Frank Kehoe]], [[Jerome Steever]], [[Edwin Swatek]], [[Bill Tuttle (swimmer)|Bill Tuttle]].<ref name=\"1904OG SR\"/> Head coach: [[Alex Meffert]].<ref name=\"Olympians\"/>\n*: [[Missouri Athletic Club]]: [[Gwynne Evans]], [[Augustus Goessling|Gus Goessling]], [[John Meyers (swimmer)|John Meyers]], [[William R. Orthwein|Bill Orthwein]], [[Amedee Reyburn]], [[Frank Schreiner]], [[Manfred Toeppen]].<ref name=\"1904OG SR\"/>\n\n* {{flagicon|BEL}} [[Water polo at the 1920 Summer Olympics|1920 Antwerp]] \u2013 4th place\n*: [[Clement Browne]], [[James Carson (water polo)|James Carson]], [[Harry Hebner]] <small>(C)</small>, [[Sophus Jensen]], [[Mike McDermott (athlete)|Mike McDermott]], [[Perry McGillivray]], [[Norman Ross]], [[Preston Steiger]], [[Herbert Taylor (swimmer)|Herbert Taylor]], [[Herb Vollmer]], [[William Vosburgh]].<ref name