er Olympics|1984]] \u2013 '''{{Silver2}} Silver medal'''\n* [[Water polo at the 1988 Summer Olympics|1988]] \u2013 '''{{Silver2}} Silver medal'''\n* [[Water polo at the 1992 Summer Olympics|1992]] \u2013 4th place\n* [[Water polo at the 1996 Summer Olympics|1996]] \u2013 7th place\n* [[Water polo at the 2000 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's tournament|2000]] \u2013 6th place\n* [[Water polo at the 2004 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's tournament|2004]] \u2013 7th place\n* [[Water polo at the 2008 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's tournament|2008]] \u2013 '''{{Silver2}} Silver medal'''\n* [[Water polo at the 2012 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's tournament|2012]] \u2013 8th place\n* [[Water polo at the 2016 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's tournament|2016]] \u2013 10th place\n* [[Water polo at the 2020 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's tournament|2020]] \u2013 ''Qualified''\n{{div col end}}\n\n====World Aquatics Championships====\n{{div col}}\n* [[Water polo at the 1973 World Aquatics Championships \u2013 Men's tournament|1973]] \u2013 5th place<ref name=\"HistoFINA\"/><ref name=\"HistoFINA PDF\"/>{{rp|15}}\n* [[Water polo at the 1975 World Aquatics Championships \u2013 Men's tournament|1975]] \u2013 8th place\n* [[Water polo at the 1978 World Aquatics Championships \u2013 Men's tournament|1978]] \u2013 5th place\n* [[Water polo at the 1982 World Aquatics Championships \u2013 Men's tournament|1982]] \u2013 6th place\n* [[Water polo at the 1986 World Aquatics Championships \u2013 Men's tournament|1986]] \u2013 4th place\n* [[Water polo at the 1991 World Aquatics Championships \u2013 Men's tournament|1991]] \u2013 4th place\n* [[Water polo at the 1994 World Aquatics Championships \u2013 Men's tournament|1994]] \u2013 6th place\n* [[Water polo at the 1998 World Aquatics Championships \u2013 Men's tournament|1998]] \u2013 7th place\n* [[Water polo at the 2001 World Aquatics Championships \u2013 Men's tournament|2001]] \u2013 7th place\n* [[Water polo at the 2003 World Aquatics Championships \u201