g]], [[Brad Schumacher]], [[Peter Stern]], [[Wolf Wigo]]. Head coach: [[John Vargas (water polo)|John Vargas]].<ref name=\"HistoFINA\"/><ref name=\"HistoFINA PDF\"/>{{rp|37}}\n\n* {{flagicon|ROU}} [[2010 FINA Men's Water Polo World Cup|2010 Oradea]] \u2013 4th place\n*: [[Merrill Moses]] <small>(GK)</small>, [[Peter Varellas]], [[Mike Sharf]], [[Jeff Powers]], [[Adam Wright (water polo)|Adam Wright]], [[Jeff Tyrell]], [[Thomas Hopkins (water polo)|Thomas Hopkins]], [[Tony Azevedo]] <small>(C)</small>, [[Ryan Bailey (water polo)|Ryan Bailey]], [[Tim Hutten]], [[Jesse Smith (water polo)|Jesse Smith]], [[Tommy Corcoran (water polo)|Tommy Corcoran]], [[Andy Stevens (water polo)|Andy Stevens]] <small>(GK)</small>. Head coach: [[Terry Schroeder]].<ref name=\"2010WCup\"/>\n\n* {{flagicon|KAZ}} [[2014 FINA Men's Water Polo World Cup|2014 Almaty]] \u2013 4th place\n*: [[McQuin Baron]] <small>(GK)</small>, [[Conner Cleary]], [[Nolan McConnell]], [[Alex Obert]], [[Alex Bowen (water polo)|Alex Bowen]], [[Bret Bonanni]], [[Josh Samuels]], [[Michael Rosenthal (water polo)|Michael Rosenthal]], [[John Mann (water polo)|John Mann]], [[Luca Cupido]], [[Jesse Smith (water polo)|Jesse Smith]], [[Ryder Roberts]], [[Merrill Moses]] <small>(GK)</small>. Head coach: [[Dejan Udovi\u010di\u0107]].<ref name=\"2014WCup\"/>\n\n* {{flagicon|GER}} [[2018 FINA Men's Water Polo World Cup|2018 Berlin]] \u2013 6th place\n*: [[McQuin Baron]] <small>(GK)</small>, [[Johnny Hooper]], [[Dylan Woodhead]], [[Alex Obert]], [[Ben Hallock]], [[Luca Cupido]], [[Nic Carniglia]], [[Alex Roelse]], [[Alex Bowen (water polo)|Alex Bowen]], [[Ben Stevenson (water polo)|Ben Stevenson]], [[Jesse Smith (water polo)|Jesse Smith]] <small>(C)</small>, [[Max Irving]], [[Jack Turner (water polo)|Jack Turner]] <small>(GK)</small>. Head coach: [[Dejan Udovi\u010di\u0107]].\n{{div col end}}\n\n====Pan American Games====\n{{main|List of United States men's national water polo team rosters#Pan American Games}}\n\n{{div col}}\n* {{